        {
            "title": "Anthropic意外洩露了Claude AI智能體的源代碼",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a> PBC意外發布了其熱門Claude AI智能體的源代碼，引發外界對其運營安全的質疑，也促使開發者試圖從中尋找這家初創公司未來計畫的線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「今天早些時候，Claude Code的發布包含了部分內部源代碼。沒有涉及或暴露任何敏感客戶數據或憑證，」Anthropic的一位發言人在一份電郵聲明中表示。「這是由人為失誤導致的發布打包問題，而非安全漏洞。我們正在推出措施，防止類似情況再次發生。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ac613f4d-979e-3104-a213-e3c639796f66-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次基礎源代碼的洩露 —— 也是該公司一周內第二次失誤事件 —— 在業界引發討論，外界由此進一步了解到這款熱門編程智能體的運作方式。開發者在X上表示，他們正在仔細研究這些細節，試圖判斷這家初創公司打算如何推進該平台的發展。多位專家也提出擔憂，認為此次意外的洩露可能帶來潛在安全漏洞。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次洩露發生前幾天，《財富》報導稱，Anthropic曾意外將數千個文件公開，其中包括一篇博客草稿。該草稿披露了一款即將推出的強大模型，其內部代號為「Mythos」和「Capybara」，並指存在網絡安全風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Anthropic Accidentally Releases Source Code for Claude AI Agent</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/anthropic%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E6%B4%A9%E9%9C%B2%E4%BA%86claude-ai%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E9%AB%94%E7%9A%84%E6%BA%90%E4%BB%A3%E7%A2%BC-084950810.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-01 17:28:58",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國股市4月開門大捷！滬指收升1.46%，收復3900點，全市場近4500股上升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aARM14UdVbhXnJ8.HgBqvw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/7ddb114ccffef963ddda6471fe114dac_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com - </strong>周三，4月1日，A股市場4月開門大捷！三大指數均升超1%，滬指收復3900點，科創50指數升超3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">今日市場單邊下行，全市場近4500只個股上升，超800只個股下跌。滬深兩市成交額2.01萬億，較上一個交易日放量199億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至收市，上證綜合指數收升1.46%，報3948.55點，深證成份指數收升1.7%，報13706.52點，創業板綜合指數收升1.96%，報3247.52點，中國A50期貨指數截稿前升1.45%，報14747點。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5758e3b2-7eaa-3014-ae12-96b074f628c6-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"580\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.Vfb9kj6Kutpn3eObtRTHw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/2c00f819d66f46ede81cf98c514b0a69\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">盤面上，醫藥板塊延續強勢，十余隻成分股升停，廣生堂、睿智醫藥20cm升停，津藥藥業4連板，潤都股份、昂利康、海王生物升停。算力硬件概念快速拉升，智立方20CM升停，續創歷史新高，瑞斯康達、銘普光磁、永鼎股份升停。算力租賃概念反復活躍，奧瑞德11天6板。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下跌方面，電力板塊走弱，廣西能源、惠天熱電跌停。高鐵軌交集體下挫，神州高鐵炸板回落，交大鐵發、通業科技跌超7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巨豐投顧郭一鳴指出，4月首個交易日，亞太市場迎來了一場酣暢淋漓的大反攻，今日A股的反彈直接受益於外部風險偏好的回暖。A股的表現雖令人欣喜，但成交量始終在2萬億附近徘徊，增量資金入場意願有限。當前A股仍處於修復行情的途中，但這是一條充滿反復與波折的路徑。外部情緒的提振為市場提供了短期支撐，但內部量能的制約決定了反彈不會一蹴而就。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>4</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>月最新</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>精選股重磅上線！</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>NVIDIA</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>有入選嗎？現在訂閱</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"480\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/24G81DjytHQBsaAyIApvLw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/10becfe8a9cfc2a9c0c4e42b4f9d7fc2\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><span><br/></span> <br/><br/></strong></p></blockquote></div>",
