            "title": "立委控減產再囤貨哄抬價格 台塑化急喊冤：此為市場因素並未減量囤貨",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NLJQ_O._wMp1V08F6ErNHw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/285f5da72c8873fe00e94185cd071ee3\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
